    <snowpackStructure>
      <comment>In the last few days sometimes deep wind slabs formed in particular in gullies and bowls and behind abrupt changes in the terrain. In gullies and bowls above approximately 1800 m a lot of snow is lying. In some places wind slabs are lying on a hard crust.</comment>
